In July 2008, she came of age and attended official ceremonies in Japan with the other members of the Imperial Family. She attended official functions at the palace and accompanied her mother to some other official events, as well as attending some on her own. On 20 March 2011, she graduated from Gakushuin University with the {{ill|Bachelor of Arts|en|Bachelor of Arts|WD=Q1765120|lt=B.A.|1=Bachelor of Arts}} degree in {{ill|Psychology|en|Psychology|WD=Q9418|lt=Psychology|1=Psychology}}.

