n of the late Princesses {{ill|Kikuko, Princess Takamatsu|en|Kikuko, Princess Takamatsu|WD=Q467655|lt=Takamatsu|1=Kikuko, Princess Takamatsu}} and {{ill|Setsuko, Princess Chichibu|en|Setsuko, Princess Chichibu|WD=Q3244162|lt=Chichibu|1=Setsuko, Princess Chichibu}} (a second cousin thrice removed and a fourth cousin thrice removed, respectively).<ref name=Senge_descent/><ref name=Nakayama_descent/>

